{
  "stem": "27507.7",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then-- but of course, those things continued, because the blockades, although that was the only time when I was actually taken in the march.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the blockades continued all the way to the-- through August.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "On my birthday, when it was 27th of August, we couldn't-- we didn't even want to stay in the shop, because we knew that it was too-- we looked every time for a different hiding hole.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know exactly--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When we looked for the different hiding hole every time, we looked for a different place every time, and we hid-- there was this cellar under the house opposite.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I think probably in [INAUDIBLE] of '49.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hid there, all spent on my birthday, 27th of August, all day in the cellar with my mother, with-- in the beginning candle, and then we didn't even have the candle, because maybe a candle came to the end.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe we were afraid even that the candle might somehow give us up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was in a cellar under some abandoned shops.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they're abandoned-- some kind of shop where-- which was already demolished, destroyed, with things thrown all over the floor, some rubbish and rubble.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the entrance was masked. the door was-- the trapdoor was masked under the things that were on the floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we spent the whole day there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we listened to the screams and the Ukrainians and Germans and so on and so forth all trampling all around us and collecting the people there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And all day in a state of complete terror.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was-- that was in '42.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was my ninth birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Tape five, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
